"title": "4209: land, spiritual aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4209: land, spiritual aspects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture presents land in a spiritual perspective. The whole earth, once perfect but now contaminated by the fall, will one day be renewed. There will be a new heaven and earth where life is abundant and God's presence is experienced for ever.</p>\n<h2>Eden: the original good land</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:8-Gen2:9\">GEN 2:8–2:9</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Paradise lost: expulsion from the garden</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19-Rom8:20\">ROM 8:19–8:20</a></p>\n<h2>The promised land: an echo of Eden</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:10\">DEU 8:7–8:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:8\">EXO 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:17\">EXO 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:5\">EXO 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:24\">LEV 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:27\">NUM 13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:3\">DEU 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:8-Deut11:12\">DEU 11:8–11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:9\">DEU 26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:3\">DEU 27:3</a></p>\n<h2>The land of Israel after the exile</h2>\n<h3>Promise of a return to the land</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:14-Amos9:15\">AMO 9:14–9:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:1\">ISA 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1-Isa35:10\">ISA 35:1–35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:41-Ezek20:42\">EZK 20:41–20:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:11-Ezek34:13\">EZK 34:11–34:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:11-Amos9:12\">AMO 9:11–9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:16-Acts15:17\">ACT 15:16–15:17</a></p>\n<h3>Promise of a restored environment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:3\">ISA 51:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:12-Zech8:13\">ZEC 8:12–8:13</a></p>\n<h2>The final restoration of the land</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">ISA 66:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:21\">ROM 8:21</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ will reign eternally over new heavens and a new earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9-Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:9–9:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:5\">MAT 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:15\">JHN 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:5\">REV 22:1–22:5</a></p>\n<h3>Vision of life on the new earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:18-Hos2:23\">HOS 2:18–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:2-Mic4:4\">MIC 4:2–4:4</a></p>\n<h2>The new Eden: the Christian's inheritance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13-Heb11:16\">HEB 11:13–11:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:5\">MAT 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:7\">REV 21:7</a>LUK <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev23:43\">23:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:1-2Cor12:4\">2CO 12:1–12:4</a></p>",
